sentence: Davis was the last Democrat until Jerry Brown in 2010 California gubernatorial election to carry Alpine, Del Norte, Sacramento, San Joaquin, and Santa Barbara Counties, the last until Jerry Brown in 2014 California gubernatorial election to carry Merced, Mono, San Diego, San Luis Obispo, Stanislaus, and Ventura Counties, and the last until Gavin Newsom in 2018 California gubernatorial election to carry San Bernardino County.
